tags.name: Sabancı Üniversitesi Sakıp Sabancı Müzesi
tags.note: Sakıp Sabancı Museum Collection of the Arts of the Book and Calligraphy have illuminated Korans, calligraphy, official documents from the Ottoman sultans, etc. Exhibits are from the end of the 14th century to the 20th century.

tags.name: Saray Tiyatrosu ve Sahne Sanatları Müzesi
Atatürk Museum, Şişli
tags.note: The museum houses personal belongings of Atatürk like clothes and collections, other than historical documents, photographs and paintings of his lifetime.
